---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { profile } from '../data/site';

const pageTitle = `${profile.name} | 博客入口`;
---

<BaseLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description="这里提供 Naloveyuki 博客的阅读入口和源码入口。"
  pathname="/blog"
>
  <main class="shell">
    <section class="panel reveal">
      <div class="page-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
        <h1>博客入口</h1>
        <p>这里整理了我的博客访问入口，以及博客源码对应的仓库地址。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="blog-grid">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <span class="meta-label">Reading</span>
          <h2>打开博客站点</h2>
          <p>如果你想看文章、随笔和更完整的个人表达，可以直接从这里进入博客。</p>
          <div class="action-row">
            <a
              class="button button-primary"
              href={profile.blog.href}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              打开博客
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card">
          <span class="meta-label">Source</span>
          <h2>查看 blog.me 仓库</h2>
          <p>如果你更关心实现细节，也可以直接查看博客源码仓库。</p>
          <div class="action-row">
            <a
              class="button button-secondary"
              href={profile.blog.repo}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              打开仓库
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
